  "content": "<!-- HTML generated using hilite.me --><div style=\"background: #202020; overflow:auto;width:auto;border:solid gray;border-width:.1em .1em .1em .8em;padding:.2em .6em;\"><pre style=\"margin: 0; line-height: 125%\"><span style=\"color: #999999; font-style: italic\">&#39; NSBasic Container Example using Leaflet Map</span>\n<span style=\"color: #999999; font-style: italic\">&#39; Magic goes here: NSBasic DIV Container becomes Leaflet DIV map</span>\n<span style=\"color: #999999; font-style: italic\">&#39; http://leafletjs.com</span>\n<span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">mapNSB</span> <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">L.map(mapContainer)</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n<!-- HTML generated using hilite.me --><div style=\"background: #202020; overflow:auto;width:auto;border:solid gray;border-width:.1em .1em .1em .8em;padding:.2em .6em;\"><pre style=\"margin: 0; line-height: 125%\"><span style=\"color: #24909d\">Function</span> <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">ShowMapJavascriptButton1_onclick()</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">JavaScript</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">mapNSB.setView([-</span><span style=\"color: #3677a9\">15.799473</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">,-</span><span style=\"color: #3677a9\">47.864167</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">],</span> <span style=\"color: #3677a9\">13</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">);</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #999999; font-style: italic\">// add an OpenStreetMap tile layer</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">L.tileLayer(</span><span style=\"color: #ed9d13\">&#39;http://{s}.tile.osm.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">,</span> <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">{</span>\n      <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">attribution:</span> <span style=\"color: #ed9d13\">&#39;&amp;copy; &lt;a href=&quot;http://osm.org/copyright&quot;&gt;OpenStreetMap&lt;/a&gt; contributors&#39;</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">}).addTo(mapNSB);</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #999999; font-style: italic\">// add a marker in the given location, attach some popup content to it and open the popup</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">L.marker([-</span><span style=\"color: #3677a9\">15.799473</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">,-</span><span style=\"color: #3677a9\">47.864167</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">]).addTo(mapNSB)</span>\n      <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">.bindPopup(</span><span style=\"color: #ed9d13\">&#39;My city :-)&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">)</span>\n      <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">.openPopup();</span>  \n  <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">End</span> <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">JavaScript</span>  \n<span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">End</span> <span style=\"color: #24909d\">Function</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n<!-- HTML generated using hilite.me --><div style=\"background: #202020; overflow:auto;width:auto;border:solid gray;border-width:.1em .1em .1em .8em;padding:.2em .6em;\"><pre style=\"margin: 0; line-height: 125%\"><span style=\"color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold\">Function</span> <span style=\"color: #447fcf\">ShowMapBasicButton2_onclick</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">()</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #999999; font-style: italic\">&#39;Try to find your location</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">mapNSB.locate({setView:</span> <span style=\"color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold\">True</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">})</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #999999; font-style: italic\">&#39;If found, fires onLocationFound function</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">mapNSB.on(</span><span style=\"color: #ed9d13\">&quot;locationfound&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">,</span> <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">onLocationFound)</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #999999; font-style: italic\">&#39;add an OpenStreetMap tile layer</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">L.tileLayer(</span><span style=\"color: #ed9d13\">&quot;http://{s}.tile.osm.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">,</span> <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">{_</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">attribution:</span> <span style=\"color: #ed9d13\">&quot;&amp;copy; &lt;a href=&#39;http://osm.org/copyright&#39;&gt;OpenStreetMap&lt;/a&gt; contributors&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">_</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">}).addTo(mapNSB)</span>\n<span style=\"color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold\">End</span> <span style=\"color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold\">Function</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold\">Function</span> <span style=\"color: #447fcf\">onLocationFound</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">(e)</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #999999; font-style: italic\">&#39;add a marker in the given location, attach some popup content To it And open the popup</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">L.marker(e.latlng).addTo(mapNSB)_</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">.bindPopup(</span><span style=\"color: #ed9d13\">&quot;Your city :-)&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">)_</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #d0d0d0\">.openPopup()</span>\n<span style=\"color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold\">End</span> <span style=\"color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold\">Function</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n", 
